-------------------
|   MathDisplay   |
-------------------
        |
        |
        |
        |
        V
-------------------
|     MathForm    |
-------------------

MathForm will be a child of MathDisplay

MathForm will send the expression to be evaluated, along with the boundaries for evaluation
Once the display gets this information, it will render the graph
Submission will be done by button click
the index component will be used to decide which type of graph will be used
